						<summary>

						<p>On one of the several stray stones placed in the verandah of the shrine of the goddess in the Kāḷahastīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Kulōttuṅga III. Year 33: 1210-11 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This mentions Āṟṟūr-nāḍu in Jayaṅgoṇḍaōḻa-maṇḍalam. The rest of the details are lost.</p>						

