<lb n="3" break="no"/>koṇṭa coḻa maṇṭalattu Āṟṟūr nāṭṭu<note n="155-1">Fragmentary. In the upper portion of the stone, there is another inscription in four lines ending with the names of the signatories. The text runs as follows:— 1 yātavarāyaneṉ ippaṭikku ivai yātavarā- 2 yan eḻuttu itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmāheśvararakṣai</hi> ivvū- 3 ruṭaṉ koṇṭu tiruvāṭṭi tirunā 4 ḷ eḻuntaruḷiviṭṭatu.</note>
